      <title>博客搭建及托管</title>
      <link href="/2025/10/28/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8F%8A%E6%89%98%E7%AE%A1/"/>
      <url>/2025/10/28/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8F%8A%E6%89%98%E7%AE%A1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、搭建流程概览"><a href="#一、搭建流程概览" class="headerlink" title="一、搭建流程概览"></a>一、搭建流程概览</h1><hr><p>1.软件及账号准备 ——&gt; 2.安装Hexo和链接github账号 ——&gt; 3.创建本地Hexo项目 ——&gt; 4.托管至github ——&gt; 5.托管至couldfare</p><hr><h1 id="二、软件及账号准备"><a href="#二、软件及账号准备" class="headerlink" title="二、软件及账号准备"></a>二、软件及账号准备</h1><h2 id="软件篇"><a href="#软件篇" class="headerlink" title="- 软件篇"></a>- 软件篇</h2><table><thead><tr><th>软件</th><th>用途</th><th>链接</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Steam++(watt toolkit)</td><td>用于加速github网站</td><td><a href="https://wwn.lanzouy.com/b01v4iz1g">蓝奏云网盘链接</a>（提取码：1234）</td></tr><tr><td>Pycharm</td><td>用于后期配置Hexo博客项目</td><td><a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/zh-cn/pycharm/download/?section=windows">官方下载链接</a>（如果失效了就去官网找）</td></tr><tr><td>Git</td><td>用于前期配置</td><td><a href="https://wwje.lanzouu.com/iokef38uwnah">蓝奏云链接</a></td></tr><tr><td>Nodejs</td><td>用于博客配置等[下载</td><td><a href="https://nodejs.cn/download/">Node.js 中文网</a></td></tr></tbody></table><p>接下来，我们检查一下git和Nodejs是否安装成功</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84lpAAFMp19A47tivIwHamK1UWnL8ukAAuIYAALQkAABVA0eRiSF4rC5NgQ.png" alt="image-1"></p><p>点击<strong>Git Bash Here</strong>，</p><p><strong>注意：在Git Bash Here里面的所有复制粘贴操作均需要按鼠标右键执行，不能用ctrl+c,ctrl+v等快捷键</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">输入:</span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">git -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果出现版本号就算安装成功</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED83hpAAFMeTWT9hbCc-xPIoIh4KXpAboAAtEYAALQkAABVAU4C9QYOsFpNgQ.png" alt="image-2"></p><p>接下来我们npm换源，用于下载加速，按下win+R,输入cmd,点击确定，在命令行里面输入：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm config set registry https://registry.npmmirror.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>无报错则安装完成！</p><h2 id="账号篇"><a href="#账号篇" class="headerlink" title="- 账号篇"></a>- 账号篇</h2><p>准备一个github账号即可，couldfare可以用github账号登录</p><p>打开steam++(也就是watt toolkit,下文直称steam++)，开启加速</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84dpAAFMoho2WxuQjh0DGbwmvjSuczAAAuAYAALQkAABVE66zxj8Igh7NgQ.png" alt="image-3"></p><p>注册github账号 <a href="https://github.com/">github官网</a>,点击<strong>sign in</strong></p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED839pAAFMhwepqx5V2SGK2MsgO-8FHlUAAtgYAALQkAABVJcKX5fBRXDENgQ.png" alt="image-4"></p><p>创建github仓库，用于储存hexo文件</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84ZpAAFMlRCAYZHPtCgFPoAXBY98xNgAAt8YAALQkAABVDR0phx-YHPQNgQ.png" alt="image-5"></p><p>注册后创建仓库名格式<strong>必须为：&lt;用户名&gt;.github.io</strong>，完成后点击<strong>create repository</strong>，这样我们的仓库就创建好了(此处设置的仓库是<strong>public</strong>类型的)</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84BpAAFMiO-SJ7DMfW9ELJ03-rdkAWwAAtkYAALQkAABVP_gkuh2UTjgNgQ.png" alt="image-6"></p><h1 id="三、安装Hexo和链接github账号"><a href="#三、安装Hexo和链接github账号" class="headerlink" title="三、安装Hexo和链接github账号"></a>三、安装Hexo和链接github账号</h1><h2 id="安装Hexo"><a href="#安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="- 安装Hexo"></a>- 安装Hexo</h2><p>打开<strong>Git Bash Here</strong>，输入：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进行安装，之后运行</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>验证是否安装成功</p><h2 id="Github部署"><a href="#Github部署" class="headerlink" title="- Github部署"></a>- Github部署</h2><p>在<strong>Git Bash Here</strong>中运行</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &lt;你的用户名&gt;</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &lt;你的邮箱&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行以下代码检查是否配置成功</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config -l</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED831pAAFMhMbUBFzmP-Vi9buR2NZNEF8AAtYYAALQkAABVB4jU_aalzNDNgQ.png" alt="image-7"></p><h2 id="连接至-GitHub"><a href="#连接至-GitHub" class="headerlink" title="- 连接至 GitHub"></a>- 连接至 GitHub</h2><p>接着运行</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &lt;你的邮箱&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>直接按几次回车生成ssh密钥，用于此电脑连接至 GitHub</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED83lpAAFMf4y4vMt8dBAWcipnHY7vU6IAAtIYAALQkAABVJD1sL1covGYNgQ.png" alt="image-8"></p><p>之后打开C盘用户文件夹下的.ssh的文件夹，用记事本打开 id_rsa.pub，复制里面的内容</p><p>然后在github主页，点右上角头像 &gt; Settings &gt; SSH and GPG keys &gt; New SSH key</p><p>Title随意，Key粘贴刚刚复制的密钥，之后点Add SSH key</p><p>运行以下代码测试连接，出现连接到账户至此环境部署完成</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>成功如图</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED83xpAAFMhJCtJj8JuwwXjTHdeOXav24AAtUYAALQkAABVJz5OtNCGh-1NgQ.png" alt="image-9"></p><h1 id="四、创建本地Hexo项目"><a href="#四、创建本地Hexo项目" class="headerlink" title="四、创建本地Hexo项目"></a>四、创建本地Hexo项目</h1><p>任意创建一个文件夹，里面用于存放Hexo项目，这里我创建my_blog文件夹</p><p>在blog文件夹里面点击鼠标右键，进入<strong>Git Bash Here</strong>，输入：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED83ppAAFMf-j5pT250l0IemJ5_5ohbowAAtMYAALQkAABVCED7CNMPWc_NgQ.png" alt="image-10"></p><p>你的my_blog文件里里面出现以下文件</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED83tpAAFMg1whwgTy6iZwNWgmZLlpIR8AAtQYAALQkAABVPRCkSi0Vy7wNgQ.png" alt="image-11"></p><p>之后输入：</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo c;hexo g;hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注意：这个段命令作用是，清理缓存（c）,产生网页（g）,本地构建博客内容(s)</strong></p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84FpAAFMi79Y1yOKkXABhS6EalZsepgAAtoYAALQkAABVKgiNG3ofeLyNgQ.png" alt="image-12"></p><p>浏览器打开 <a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a> 测试网站，出现以下界面说明Hexo项目创建成功，按下ctrl+c停止</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84hpAAFMpuA8oGp5D8mFa4vZ45kMHBAAAuEYAALQkAABVEN4zZvvG6O6NgQ.png" alt="image-13"></p><h1 id="五、托管至github"><a href="#五、托管至github" class="headerlink" title="五、托管至github"></a>五、托管至github</h1><p>在<strong>Git Bash Here</strong>中输入以下内容，用于安装 hexo-deployer-git</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在my_blog文件夹内，修改 _config.yml 文件 deploy 部分（文件最下面）,之后保存</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repository:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:&lt;用户名&gt;/&lt;用户名&gt;.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>运行以下命令，将代码部署到 GitHub，执行hexo d时候也要<strong>关闭steam++</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo cl; hexo g; hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="六、托管至couldfare"><a href="#六、托管至couldfare" class="headerlink" title="六、托管至couldfare"></a>六、托管至couldfare</h1><p>先注册一下couldfare的账号，直接用刚才连接了的github注册，过程可能会较慢，请耐心等待。</p><p>进入主页后，按以下顺序点击：</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84RpAAFMkGJwvS8oUitlR_VgFWyr9k8AAt0YAALQkAABVH4h3vT9uuMBNgQ.png" alt="image-14"></p><p>点击<strong>Connect Github</strong>，之后按如下操作</p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED835pAAFMh4S-bu2A6rMG-ahiCFN1g-UAAtcYAALQkAABVPgOgqbP90mONgQ.png" alt="image-15"></p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84NpAAFMkHRLFZfGyncxCdYUJSIwU8wAAtwYAALQkAABVMmaWyfmgDPaNgQ.png" alt="image-16"></p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84JpAAFMjmnINqKucs5Loxy5EiZMV0UAAtsYAALQkAABVJu_a-hzfU8wNgQ.png" alt="image-17"></p><p>以下链接就是你的博客链接，可以点击访问了 </p><p><img src="https://img.remit.ee/api/file/BQACAgUAAyEGAASHRsPbAAED84VpAAFMldAd8_Ygn_pL3nzb3LQkF3IAAt4YAALQkAABVG0XegMLIJ0vNgQ.png" alt="image-18"></p><p>[^1 ]:  参考文章：<a href="https://www.xmdblog.com/posts/70db7d7c.html">Hexo博客搭建教程 | 小明的部落格</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
